400461,99,293,13,47,1,237,32,"Tattha sakalābhe atittassa paralābhe patthanā atricchatā nāma, yāya samannāgatassa ekabhājane pakkapūvepi attano patte patite na supakko viya khuddako ca viya khāyati, sveva pana parassa patte pakkhitto supakko viya mahanto viya ca khāyati. "
