403808,99,987,2,2,1,19,1,Sobhitattheravatthu 
403809,99,988,2,16,1,120,10,227. Pañcame pubbenivāsaṃ anussarantānan ti pubbe nivutthakkhandhasantānaṃ anussaraṇasamatthānaṃ sobhitatthero aggoti dasseti. 
403810,99,988,17,33,1,139,15,So kira pubbenivāsaṃ anupaṭipāṭiyā anussaramāno pañca kappasatāni asaññibhave acittakapaṭisandhiṃ nayato aggahesi ākāse padaṃ dassento viya. 
403811,99,988,34,40,1,48,6,Tasmā pubbenivāsaṃ anussarantānaṃ aggo nāma jāto. 
403812,99,989,2,31,1,286,27,Tassa pañhakamme ayamanupubbikathā– ayampi kira padumuttarabuddhakāle haṃsavatīnagare kulagehe paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhitvā vayappatto satthu dhammadesanaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ pubbenivāsañāṇalābhīnaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā adhikārakammaṃ katvā taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthesi. 
403813,99,989,32,48,1,137,15,"So yāvajīvaṃ kusalakammaṃ katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbatti, sobhito tissa nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
403814,99,990,2,18,1,143,15,So aparena samayena satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ patvā pubbenivāsañāṇe ciṇṇavasī ahosi. 
403815,99,990,19,31,1,111,11,"So anupaṭipāṭiyā attano nibbattaṭṭhānaṃ anussaranto yāva asaññibhave acittakapaṭisandhi, tāva paṭisandhiṃ addasa. "
403816,99,990,32,60,1,150,20,Tato paraṃ antare pañca kappasatāni pavattiṃ adisvā avasāne cutiṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ nāmetan’’ ti āvajjamāno nayavasena‘‘ asaññibhavo bhavissatī’’ ti niṭṭhaṃ agamāsi. 
403817,99,990,61,71,1,94,10,Satthā imaṃ kāraṇaṃ aṭṭhuppattiṃ katvā theraṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarantānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapesīti. 
403818,99,991,2,2,1,17,1,Upālittheravatthu 
403819,99,992,2,16,1,91,9,228. Chaṭṭhe vinayadharānaṃ yadidaṃ {upālī}ti vinayadharānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ upālitthero aggoti dasseti. 
403820,99,992,17,27,1,92,10,Thero kira tathāgatasseva santike kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
403821,99,992,28,49,1,171,14,"Tathāgatasseva santike vinayapiṭakaṃ uggaṇhitvā bhārukacchakavatthuṃ, ajjukavatthuṃ,( pārā.158) kumārakassapavatthunti imāni tīṇi vatthūni sabbaññutaññāṇena saddhiṃ saṃsandetvā kathesi. "
403822,99,992,50,55,1,35,5,Tasmā vinayadharānaṃ aggo nāma jāto. 
403823,99,993,2,27,1,246,24,Tassa pañhakamme ayamanupubbikathā– padumuttarabuddhakāle kiresa haṃsavatiyaṃ kulaghare nibbatto ekadivasaṃ satthu dhammakathaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ vinayadharānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā adhikārakammaṃ katvā taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthesi. 
403824,99,993,28,44,1,131,14,"So yāvajīvaṃ kusalaṃ katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kappakagehe paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi , upālidārakotissa nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
403825,99,993,45,63,1,163,17,So vayappatto channaṃ khattiyānaṃ pasādhako hutvā tathāgate anupiyambavane viharante pabbajjatthāya nikkhamantehi teti chahi khattiyehi saddhiṃ nikkhamitvā pabbaji. 
