403827,99,994,2,21,1,103,12,"So pabbajitvā upasampanno satthāraṃ kammaṭṭhānaṃ kathāpetvā‘‘ mayhaṃ, bhante, araññavāsaṃ anujānāthā’’ ti āha. "
403828,99,994,22,37,1,138,14,"Bhikkhu tava araññe vasantassa ekameva dhuraṃ vaḍḍhissati, amhākaṃ pana santike vasantassa vipassanādhurañca ganthadhurañca paripūressatīti. "
