403833,99,995,2,2,1,19,1,Nandakattheravatthu 
403834,99,996,2,21,1,132,14,229. Sattame bhikkhunovādakānaṃ yadidaṃ {nandako}ti ayaṃ hi thero dhammakathaṃ kathento ekasamodhāne pañca bhikkhunīsatāni arahattaṃ pāpesi. 
403835,99,996,22,27,1,39,5,Tasmā bhikkhunovādakānaṃ aggo nāma jāto. 
403836,99,997,2,26,1,242,23,Tassa pañhakamme ayamanupubbikathā– ayañhi padumuttarabuddhakāle haṃsavatīnagare kulagehe nibbatto satthu dhammadesanaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ bhikkhunovādakānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā adhikārakammaṃ katvā taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthesi. 
