403966,99,1013,128,162,1,201,24,"Satthā‘‘ pubbe ime cīvaradānassa dinnattā attano pattacīvarāni gahetvāva āgatā’’ ti suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ hatthaṃ pasāretvā‘‘ etha bhikkhavo, svākkhāto dhammo, caratha brahmacariyaṃ sammā dukkhassa antakiriyāyā’’ ti āha. "
