403994,99,1019,2,2,1,18,1,Sāgatattheravatthu 
403995,99,1020,2,16,1,90,9,232. Dasame tejodhātukusalānan ti tejodhātuṃ samāpajjituṃ kusalānaṃ sāgatatthero aggoti dasseti. 
403996,99,1020,17,28,1,107,11,Ayañhi thero tejodhātusamāpattiyā ambatitthanāgassa tejasā tejaṃ pariyādiyitvā taṃ nāgaṃ nibbisevanaṃ akāsi. 
403997,99,1020,29,35,1,39,5,Tasmā tejodhātukusalānaṃ aggo nāma jāto. 
403998,99,1021,2,28,1,263,25,Tassa pañhakamme ayamanupubbikathā– ayampi hi padumuttarabuddhakāle haṃsavatiyaṃ kulagehe paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā aparabhāge satthudhammadesanaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ tejodhātukusalānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā adhikārakammaṃ katvā taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthesi. 
403999,99,1021,29,44,1,136,14,"So yāvajīvaṃ kusalaṃ katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbatti, sāgatamāṇavotissa nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
404000,99,1021,45,58,1,123,13,So aparabhāge satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā aṭṭha samāpattiyo nibbattetvā tattha vasībhāvaṃ pāpuṇi. 
404001,99,1022,2,8,1,66,6,Athekadivasaṃ satthā cārikaṃ caramāno kosambinagarasamīpaṃ agamāsi. 
404002,99,1022,9,21,1,101,12,Tena ca samayena nadītitthe porāṇakanāvikassa bahū āgantukagamikā verino hutvā taṃ pothetvā mārayiṃsu. 
404003,99,1022,22,33,1,97,11,So viruddhena cittena patthanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā tasmiṃyeva titthe mahānubhāvo nāgarājā hutvā nibbatto. 
404004,99,1022,34,48,1,91,12,"So viruddhacittattā akāleyeva vassāpeti, kāle pana na vassāpeti, sassāni na sammā sampajjanti. "
404005,99,1022,49,63,1,115,12,"Sakalaraṭṭhavāsino ca tassa vūpasamanatthaṃ anusaṃvaccharaṃ balikammaṃ karonti, vasanatthāya cassa ekaṃ gehaṃ akaṃsu. "
404006,99,1022,64,79,1,102,11,Satthāpi teneva titthena uttaritvā bhikkhusaṅghaparivuto‘‘ tasmiṃyeva padese rattiṃ vasissāmī’’ ti agamāsi. 
404007,99,1023,2,33,1,197,23,Athāyaṃ thero‘‘ caṇḍo kirettha nāgarājā’’ ti sutvā‘‘ imaṃ nāgarājānaṃ dametvā nibbisevanaṃ katvā satthu vasanaṭṭhānaṃ pariyādetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti nāgarājassa vasanaṭṭhānaṃ pavisitvā pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā nisīdi. 
404008,99,1023,34,53,1,108,13,"Nāgo kujjhitvā‘‘ konāmāyaṃ muṇḍako mayhaṃ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ pavisitvā nisinno’’ ti dhūpāyi, thero uttaritaraṃ dhūpāyi. "
404009,99,1023,54,64,1,66,8,"Nāgo, pajjali, theropi uttaritaraṃ pajjalitvā tassa tejaṃ pariyādiyi. "
404010,99,1023,65,90,1,97,14,"So‘‘ mahanto vatāyaṃ bhikkhū’’ ti therassa pādamūle nipatitvā,‘‘ bhante, tumhākaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmī’’ ti āha. "
404011,99,1023,91,98,1,61,6,"Mayhaṃ saraṇagamanakiccaṃ natthi, dasabalassa saraṇaṃ gacchāti. "
404012,99,1023,99,121,1,111,16,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti saraṇagato hutvā tato paṭṭhāya na kañci viheṭheti, devampi sammā vassāpeti, sassāni sammā sampajjanti. "
404013,99,1024,2,20,1,131,14,Kosambivāsino ‘‘ ayyena kira sāgatena ambatitthakanāgo damito’’ ti sutvā satthu āgamanaṃ udikkhamānā dasabalassa mahāsakkāraṃ sajjayiṃsu. 
404014,99,1024,21,41,1,177,19,Te dasabalassa mahāsakkāraṃ katvā chabbaggiyānaṃ vacanena sabbagehesu kāpotikaṃ pasannaṃ paṭiyādetvā punadivase sāgatattherassa piṇḍāya carantassa gehe gehe thokaṃ thokaṃ adaṃsu. 
404015,99,1024,42,60,1,151,17,Thero apaññatte sikkhāpade manussehi yāciyamāno gehe gehe thokaṃ thokaṃ pivitvā avidūraṃ gantvāva anāhārikabhāvena satiṃ vissajjetvā saṅkāraṭṭhāne pati. 
404016,99,1025,2,13,1,103,11,Satthā katabhattakicco nikkhamanto taṃ disvā gāhāpetvā vihāraṃ gantvā vigarahitvā sikkhāpadaṃ paññāpesi. 
404017,99,1025,14,30,1,143,16,So punadivase satiṃ labhitvā attanā katakāraṇaṃ sutvā accayaṃ desetvā dasabalaṃ khamāpetvā uppannasaṃvego vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
