404059,99,1032,90,103,1,132,13,Athassa vaṇamukhaṃ pīḷetvā pubbalohitaṃ nīharitvā kasāvodakena dhovitvā attano jānanabhesajjaṃ makkhetvā nacirasseva phāsukaṃ akaṃsu. 
