404065,99,1033,77,83,1,45,5,Hatthipotako pitu pacchato pacchato anupāyāsi. 
404066,99,1033,84,91,1,68,7,Hatthināgo tassa āgatabhāvaṃ ñatvā nivattanatthāya saddasaññaṃ adāsi. 
404067,99,1033,92,100,1,57,8,So pitu kathaṃ sutvā nivattitvā vaḍḍhakīnaṃ santikaṃ gato. 
404068,99,1033,101,130,1,154,20,"Vaḍḍhakino‘‘ imaṃ hatthipotakaṃ amhākaṃ dātuṃ āgato bhavissati eso’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ amhākaṃ santike tayā kattabbakiccaṃ natthi, pitu santikaṃyeva gacchā’’ ti pahiṇiṃsu. "
404069,99,1033,131,140,1,83,9,Hatthināgo yāvatatiyaṃ attano santikaṃ āgatampi puna vaḍḍhakīnaṃyeva samīpaṃ pesesi. 
404070,99,1033,141,149,1,72,8,Tato paṭṭhāya vaḍḍhakino hatthipotakaṃ attano santike katvā paṭijagganti. 
404071,99,1033,150,159,1,69,8,"Bhojanakāle ekekaṃ bhattapiṇḍaṃ denti, bhattaṃ tassa yāvadatthaṃ ahosi. "
404072,99,1033,160,169,1,83,9,So vaḍḍhakīhi antogahane koṭṭitaṃ dabbasambhāraṃ āharitvā aṅgaṇaṭṭhāne rāsiṃ karoti. 
404073,99,1033,170,175,1,45,5,Eteneva niyāmena aññampi upakārakammaṃ karoti. 
