404082,99,1039,2,2,1,21,1,Mogharājattheravatthu 
404083,99,1040,2,14,1,82,8,234. Dvādasame lūkhacīvaradharānan ti lūkhacīvaraṃ dhārentānaṃ mogharājā aggoti dasseti. 
404084,99,1040,15,26,1,105,11,Ayaṃ hi thero satthalūkhaṃ suttalūkhaṃ rajanalūkhanti tividhenapi lūkhena samannāgataṃ paṃsukūlaṃ dhāresi. 
404085,99,1040,27,32,1,40,5,Tasmā lūkhacīvaradharānaṃ aggo nāma jāto. 
404086,99,1041,2,33,1,278,28,"Tassa pañhakamme ayamanupubbikathā– ayampi hi padumuttarabuddhakāle haṃsavatiyaṃ kulagehe paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā nibbatti, tato aparabhāge satthu dhammakathaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ lūkhacīvaradharānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā adhikārakammaṃ katvā taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthesi. "
404087,99,1041,34,48,1,142,13,So yāvajīvaṃ kusalaṃ katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto kassapadasabalassa nibbattito puretarameva kaṭṭhavāhananagare amaccagehe paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
404088,99,1041,49,55,1,74,6,Aparabhāge vayappatto kaṭṭhavāhanarājānaṃ upaṭṭhahanto amaccaṭṭhānaṃ labhi. 
404089,99,1042,2,7,1,40,5,Tasmiṃ kāle kassapadasabalo loke uppajji. 
404090,99,1042,8,22,1,71,10,Kaṭṭhavāhanarājā‘‘ buddho kira loke uppanno’’ ti sutvā taṃ pakkosāpetvā āha–
404091,99,1042,23,59,1,226,29,"‘‘ tāta, buddho kira loke uppanno, imaṃ paccantanagaraṃ ekappahāreneva ubhohi amhehi tucchaṃ kātuṃ na sakkā, tvaṃ tāva majjhimadesaṃ gantvā buddhassa uppannabhāvaṃ ñatvā dasabalaṃ imaṃ nagaraṃ ānehī’’ ti purisasahassena saddhiṃ pesesi. "
404092,99,1042,60,74,1,134,14,So anupubbena satthu santikaṃ gantvā dhammakathaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho tattheva pabbajitvā vīsati vassasahassāni samaṇadhammaṃ akāsi. 
404093,99,1042,75,85,1,73,10,Tena saddhiṃ gatapurisā pana sabbepi nivattitvā puna rañño santikaṃ āgatā. 
404094,99,1043,2,24,1,200,20,"Ayaṃ thero paripuṇṇasīlo kālaṃ katvā ekaṃ buddhantaraṃ devamanussesu saṃsaranto amhākaṃ dasabalassa nibbattito puretarameva sāvatthiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi, mogharājamāṇavotissa nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
404095,99,1043,25,47,1,232,21,"Kaṭṭhavāhanarājāpi kassapassa bhagavato adhikārakammaṃ katvā ekaṃ buddhantaraṃ saparivāro devamanussesu saṃsaritvā amhākaṃ dasabalassa nibbattito puretarameva sāvatthiyaṃ purohitagehe paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi, bāvarimāṇavotissa nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
404096,99,1043,48,59,1,92,11,So aparena samayena tayo vede uggaṇhitvā soḷasannaṃ māṇavakasahassānaṃ sippaṃ vācento carati. 
404097,99,1043,60,67,1,69,7,Athassa pasenadikosalarañño kāle pitu accayena purohitaṭṭhānaṃ adaṃsu. 
404098,99,1043,68,75,1,68,7,Tadā ayampi mogharājamāṇavo bāvaribrāhmaṇassa santike sippaṃ gaṇhāti. 
404099,99,1044,2,28,1,202,21,Athekadivasaṃ bāvaribrāhmaṇo rahogato attano sippe sāraṃ olokento samparāyikaṃ sāraṃ adisvā‘‘ ekaṃ pabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā samparāyikaṃ gavesessāmī’’ ti kosalarājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā attano pabbajjaṃ anujānāpesi. 
404100,99,1044,29,37,1,76,8,So tena anuññāto soḷasahi māṇavakasahassehi parivuto pabbajjatthāya nikkhami. 
