404103,99,1044,62,77,1,147,14,Bāvaribrāhmaṇo phāsukaṭṭhānaṃ olokento majjhimadesato paṭikkamma assakarañño ca muḷhakarañño ca sīmantare godhāvaritīre attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃ kāresi. 
