404105,99,1045,16,23,1,50,7,Tena kataṃ disvā aparaṃ kulasataṃ gehasataṃ kāresi. 
404106,99,1045,24,53,1,175,22,"Te sabbepi sannipatitvā‘‘ mayaṃ ayyānaṃ santake bhūmibhāge vasāma, mudhā vasituṃ na kāraṇaṃ, sukhavāsaṃ vo dassāmā’’ ti ekeko ekekaṃ kahāpaṇaṃ bāvaribrāhmaṇassa vasanaṭṭhāne ṭhapesi. "
