404164,99,1056,2,18,1,100,9,235. Theripāḷiyā paṭhame yadidaṃ {mahāpajāpatigotamī}ti mahāpajāpatigotamī therī rattaññūnaṃ aggāti dasseti. 
404165,99,1057,2,32,1,271,28,Tassā pañhakamme pana ayamanupubbikathā– ayaṃ kira padumuttarabuddhakāle haṃsavatiyaṃ kulagehe paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhitvā aparena samayena satthu dhammadesanaṃ suṇantī satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuniṃ rattaññūnaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā adhikārakammaṃ katvā taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthesi. 
