404977,99,1216,2,2,1,12,1,Jīvakavatthu 
404978,99,1217,2,16,1,108,10,256. Navame puggalappasannānan ti puggaliyappasādena samannāgatānaṃ upāsakānaṃ jīvako komārabhacco aggoti dasseti. 
404979,99,1217,17,24,1,58,6,So hi padumuttarabuddhakāle haṃsavatiyaṃ kulagehe nibbatto . 
404980,99,1217,25,40,1,143,15,Satthu dhammakathaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ upāsakaṃ puggalappasannānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā adhikārakammaṃ katvā taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthesi. 
404981,99,1217,41,55,1,156,14,So kappasatasahassaṃ devamanussesu saṃsaritvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde rājagahanagare abhayarājakumāraṃ paṭicca sālavatiyā nāma rūpūpajīviniyā kucchimhi nibbatto. 
404982,99,1217,56,65,1,59,8,"Rūpūpajīviniyo ca nāma vijātakāle sace putto hoti, chaḍḍenti. "
404983,99,1217,66,70,1,23,3,"Sace dhītā, paṭijagganti. "
404984,99,1217,71,78,1,58,7,Iti sā taṃ dārakaṃ kattarasuppakena saṅkārakūṭe chaḍḍāpesi. 
404985,99,1217,79,109,1,130,19,"Atha naṃ abhayo rājakumāro rājupaṭṭhānaṃ gacchanto taṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ, bhaṇe, etaṃ kākehi samparikiṇṇan’’ ti manusse pesetvā‘‘ dārako devā’’ ti. "
404986,99,1217,110,126,1,60,9,"Jīvati, bhaṇeti,‘‘ jīvati, devā’’ ti sutvā attano antepure posāpesi. "
404987,99,1217,127,139,1,95,11,"Tassa jīvatīti kathitattā jīvakoti nāmaṃ akaṃsu, kumārena posāpitoti komārabhaccoti nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
404988,99,1218,2,18,1,157,16,So attano soḷasavassuddesikakāle takkasilaṃ gantvā vejjasippaṃ uggaṇhitvā bimbisārarañño santikā sakkāraṃ labhitvā caṇḍapajjotassa rañño rogaṃ phāsukaṃ akāsi. 
