405321,99,1272,37,61,1,100,15,Tato seṭṭhi‘‘ evaṃ taṃ gāvo madditvā māressantī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ imaṃ dārakaṃ vajadvāre nipajjāpethā’’ ti āha. 
405322,99,1272,62,65,1,23,3,Taṃ tattha nipajjāpesuṃ. 
