405338,99,1275,57,73,1,150,16,Seṭṭhi dārakassa papātato patitaṭṭhāne matabhāvaṃ vā amatabhāvaṃ vā pariyesāpento naḷakārajeṭṭhakena gahitabhāvaṃ ñatvā tassapi sahassaṃ datvā āṇāpesi. 
