409033,100,417,72,89,1,157,16,"Yo pana appamattakena byādhinā samannāgato labhantopi alabhantopi vuṭṭhātiyeva, tassa vināpi bhesajjena vūpasamanabyādhi bhesajje kate khippataraṃ vūpasammati. "
409034,100,417,90,101,1,82,10,"So tato buddhavacanaṃ vā uggaṇhituṃ sakkhissati, samaṇadhammaṃ vā kātuṃ sakkhissati. "
