409040,100,418,37,46,1,70,8,"Tatiyavārena vipañcitaññū puggalo kathito, neyyo pana tannissitova hoti. "
409041,100,419,2,10,1,63,7,Dhammadesanā {anuññātā}ti māsassa aṭṭha vāre dhammakathā anuññātā. 
409042,100,419,11,18,1,57,6,Aññesampi dhammo {desetabbo}ti itaresampi dhammo kathetabbo. 
409043,100,419,19,21,1,10,2,Kiṃ kāraṇā? 
409044,100,419,22,32,1,98,10,Padaparamassa hi imasmiṃ attabhāve dhammaṃ paṭivijjhituṃ asakkontassāpi anāgate paccayo bhavissati. 
