409104,100,429,2,53,1,346,41,"Evameva {kho}ti ettha idaṃ opammasaṃsandanaṃ– duṭṭhāruko viya hi kodhanapuggalo, tassa attano dhammatāya savanaṃ viya kodhanassapi attano dhammatāya uddhumātassa viya caṇḍikatassa caraṇaṃ, kaṭṭhena vā kaṭhalāya vā ghaṭṭanaṃ viya appamattaṃ vacanaṃ, bhiyyosomattāya savanaṃ viya‘‘ mādisaṃ nāma esa evaṃ vadatī’’ ti bhiyyosomattāya uddhumāyanabhāvo daṭṭhabbo. "
